Download the SwiftMailer library and unpack the files directly in this folder:

http://swiftmailer.org/

This folder should contain:

[directory] classes (the core SwiftMailer classes)
[directory] dependency_maps
[file] mime_types.php
[file] preferences.php
[file] swift_init.php
[file] swift_required.php
[file] swift_required_pear.php